sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Usuário (App)
    participant Backend as Seu Backend (Node/Go/Python)
    participant MP as Mercado Pago API
    participant Firebase as Firebase Admin SDK

    User->>Backend: Solicita Upgrade (Checkout)
    Backend->>MP: Cria Assinatura (Pre-approval)
    MP-->>Backend: Retorna Link de Pagamento/Status
    Backend-->>User: Redireciona para Pagamento
    User->>MP: Realiza Pagamento
    MP-->>Backend: Webhook (Payment/Subscription Update)
    Backend->>MP: GET /preapproval/{id} (Valida origem/status)
    Backend->>Firebase: setCustomUserClaims(uid, {plan: 'plus'})
    Backend-->>User: Notifica Sucesso (WebSocket/Poll)
    User->>Firebase: Force Refresh Token (Novas Claims)